    "Writing is the optimum medium for demonstration of disciplinary practice and complex, holistic knowledge.",
    "Heavy-handed proctoring of written exams is one reaction, but not the solution when disciplinary work nowadays requires formal citation and reference to social knowledge much wider than that which can be retained in long term memory for the test.More broadly still, Generative AI also throws education into crisis.",
